featured_reviews.review_id: This is one of the oldest Masjid of meerapur. This is a land mark. People know the near by land by the name of Thawar wali masjid. The mosque is located in the main market and near main highway, which is easily accessible by public transport. People come here and offer NAMAZ. People find the real peace of mind here. They sit for some time after NAMAZ here and feel the inner peace. Really if you want some peace of mind, just go to Masjid, offer NAMAZ and sit there for some alone, you will feel the inner peace.
